synopsis.text: Nagare Hisui, known as the Green King, is the enigmatic founder of JUNGLE, an SNS app that bestows unnatural power and abilities to its users. Sukuna Gojo, a young man who fled his affluent yet stifling home, has been surviving on the streets, relying on JUNGLE's powers to navigate through life. Intrigued by the elusive Green King, Sukuna embarks on a mission to climb the ranks of JUNGLE, aiming to meet Hisui in person. However, the journey to the top is fraught with challenges, as Sukuna must confront and defeat the most formidable user in JUNGLE to achieve the highest rank. Will Sukuna's determination and newfound abilities pave the way for a fateful encounter with the Green King? Join Sukuna in this thrilling adventure to find out!
